root: ^Hm... Mediocre at best, you little pests!
^Are you sure? I think I saw some evens in there!
^Hm-hm... Don't you want to know I rounded all these numbers?...
^So thoughtful, mister wizard! We'd love to stay but we were just on our way out.
^Should we get going, Twootie? I'll need your help though.
^Numbers, I think it's prime time we teach these fools a lesson!
